name: Virginia Secretary of the Commonwealth
tweet: Thank you for sharing, @CarahOng! Dr. Carah Ong Whaley is one of our incredible Virginia Complete Count Commissioners and has been working on hard to make sure all Virginians are counted in the 2020 Census. We are so lucky to have you on the Commission! #VACompleteCount

tweet: @ndngenuity Good morning, thank you for your message. All of our engagement calls are open to the general public! We hope you can join us.

name: Virginia Secretary of the Commonwealth
tweet: Thank you to everyone who attended the 342nd Annual Indian Tax Tribute ceremony (despite the rain!) today. We are so happy and proud to take part in honoring this tradition from 1677 with the Pamunkey and Mattaponi Indian Tribes.  https://t.co/kAYCLckVWA

name: Virginia Secretary of the Commonwealth
tweet: REMINDER: The 342nd Annual Indian Tax Tribute ceremony is tomorrow at 10:00 a.m. at the @VAGovMansion.   This event marks the anniversary of the Treaty of Middle Plantation - honoring the promise between the Mattaponi and Pamunkey Indian Tribes and the Commonwealth of Virginia.  https://t.co/S3Vyy9vl4d
